description:
Here we present the Encyclopedia of RNA Interactomes (ENCORI), a comprehensive atlas integrating precise RNA interactions identified by our innovative rbsSeeker and rriScan algorithms, showcasing massive mechanistic insights into RNA interactomes from CLIP-seq and RNA interactome sequencing data. ENCORI systematically provides millions of high-confidence RNA interactions, &nbsp;revealing the complexity of gene regulation. Through this resource, we predicted and validated a novel N6-methyladenosine reader and an orphan snoRNA guiding rRNA modification, demonstrating its pivotal role in advancing RNA research. 
 &nbsp; 


 This repository contains the source codes of our innovative rbsSeeker and rriScan software, as well as codes for generating the figures and their related analysis data.

